{"tid":1335350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係街見到小朋友...有無同我一樣嘅感覺","createTime":"2019-07-20T13:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:43:07.000Z","uid":109358,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aedcb3c17d414d9cfeab050e369d5dec3cd31fce","tid":1335350,"uid":109358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"而家撘車又好 係街又好 <br />\n見到小朋友都會有種好心酸嘅感覺 <br />\n雖然自己年紀唔大 <br />\n自己都未叫係照顧到自己 <br />\n亦唔好話有能力照顧到其他人<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好驚佢地會係香港呢個地方失去自由 好驚佢地大個無擁有自己思想呢啲咁基本嘅權利 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想盡我少少嘅綿力 為佢地做啲野<br />\n<br />\n我地呢一代 身於亂世 有種責任 <br />\n<br />\n為左下一代 <br />\n<br />\n你聽日唔係唔出黎啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CLqftm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CLqftm.png&h=5241e57c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3566a59036da5b484709c432605ecea29f3206b2","tid":1335350,"uid":109358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爭取雙普選</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">脫離中共管治</span></span>"},{"pid":"79682869ebe89a425d33ddcae20aa7d130afdfbf","tid":1335350,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57eb0a11a98229ee4539d32c917bff4c29b9853e","tid":1335350,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79682869ebe89a425d33ddcae20aa7d130afdfbf","tid":1335350,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"死返支那啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"d49322d0e10c37c3f883745de00d1ffc426857be","tid":1335350,"uid":109358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79682869ebe89a425d33ddcae20aa7d130afdfbf","tid":1335350,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cite